Abolished 31.3.1896 to become the separate parishes of Ashington 
    and Sheepwash.
Abolished 1.4.1935 and added to the parish of Ashington.
Abolished 24.3.1888 and divided between the parishes of Morpeth and Newminster Abbey.

Abolished 1.4.1935 and added to the parish of Thirston with 
    Shothaugh. See also Table 2, note (a).
Abolished 1.4.1914 and added to the parish of Ashington.

Abolished 1.4.1935 and divided between the parishes of Morpeth 
    and Hepscott.

Abolished 30.9.1894 and divided between the parishes of Newminster 
    and Morpeth.

Abolished 1.4.1935 and added to the parish of Newbiggin by 
    the Sea.

Abolished 30.9.1894 and divided between the parishes of Tranwell 
    and Morpeth.

Abolished 1.4.1935 and divided between the parishes of Ashington 
    and Newbiggin by the Sea.
